channel.title: Need coder to help me get my RSPS online
channel.description:
Hey is there anyone who's good at coding? I've been trying to start my own RSPS for a while now, and I finally figured out the main stuff, and I can play it, but I want to get it public for other people, except i'm having problems with my Run Server.
If you have TeamViewer and Skype, we can use that to work/communicate. It would be a giant help, and i'd really appreciate it. This is my first server.
If you can help, just comment and let me know your skype and stuff and i'll add you! Thanks! :D
